<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,258,1509]" pageId="10" pageNumber="79">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,501,1125,1150]" pageId="10" pageNumber="79">Ecology and distribution.</emphasis>
Specimens were obtained from pine and oak litter and from herbaceous vegetation. They all have a gut content composed mainly of fungal hyphae and spores.
</paragraph>
